{
  "id": "adv_event_2212_01_05",
  "title": "生まれて\nきてくれて\nありがとう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスパーティー開始から数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few hours after the Christmas party",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.0999999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "プレゼント交換会を終えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the gift exchange",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1,
      "endTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "はー、美味しかったー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ that was delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6,
      "endTime": 10.445237922699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は月ストの単独ライブにクリスマスパーティーと\nとても濃い一日でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today was a packed day with Moon Tempest's solo live\nand the Christmas party.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6666666667,
      "endTime": 17.4838658651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の琴乃のきょとんとした顔……\n何度でも思い出したくなりますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That surprised look on Kotono's face at that time…\nI want to remember it over and over again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7,
      "endTime": 23.2333388358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "もう……本当にびっくりしたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really… I was so surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4333333333,
      "endTime": 26.8676042397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.0666666667,
      "endTime": 29.0386394183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　渚、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Nagisa-chan‚ what's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2333333333,
      "endTime": 33.0777082761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん。本番はこれからだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan. The main event is from now on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2666666667,
      "endTime": 35.9620633761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "私達四人から、琴乃ちゃんへプレゼントがあります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We four have a present for you‚ Kotono-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1666666667,
      "endTime": 40.1665532271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも、みんなからプレゼントはもうもらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But I already received presents from everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3666666667,
      "endTime": 45.3086668651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "先ほどのプレゼントはあくまで私達からの\n個別のプレゼントですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The previous gifts were\nindividual ones from us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5,
      "endTime": 50.6857248465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "今度のプレゼントはねー、四人で作ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This next present‚ you see‚ was made by the four of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8666666667,
      "endTime": 54.6816779773,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7093.333333300002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "四人で作る？　それってどういう……あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Made by four? What do you mean… ah",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9,
      "endTime": 60.7004377365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "これって……アルバム？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this… an album?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9,
      "endTime": 64.4795000076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　星見市にいた頃からつい最近までの\n記録を徹底的にまとめたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! It's a thorough compilation of our records\nfrom our time in Hoshimi City to just recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6666666667,
      "endTime": 70.8561079492,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6400.0000000000055
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11366.666666600011
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……これは初めてライブをした時の……\nあ、こっちはNEXT VENUSグランプリ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… this is from our first live show…\nAh‚ this is the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0666666667,
      "endTime": 79.76203007960001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8899.99999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　レッスンの休憩中……？\nこんな写真いつの間に……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? During a break in a lesson…?\nWhen was this photo taken…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9666666667,
      "endTime": 87.723931635,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7933.333333300013
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　これって……さっきのライブの\nサプライズ？　いつの間にまとめたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? This is… from the surprise at today's live?\nWhen was it compiled?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9,
      "endTime": 95.9970730305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも手伝って\nくれたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san helped us\nput it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2,
      "endTime": 98.4014047821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、サプライズの時の写真で\n何か気付くことない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ do you notice anything about the photos\nfrom the surprise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6,
      "endTime": 103.97905435199999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "気付くこと……あ、私が喋ってる時の\n写真の角度が違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Notice something… ah‚ the angle of the photo\nwhere I'm speaking is different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1666666667,
      "endTime": 112.9531801352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "一枚は正面から撮ってて、もう一枚は……\n舞台袖から撮ってる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One is taken from the front‚ and the other is…\nfrom the side of the stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1666666667,
      "endTime": 120.49516526369999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "正解ですわ！　{user}さんが見事に\n責務を果たしてくれましたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Correct! {user}-san splendidly\nfulfilled his duty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7,
      "endTime": 125.99076472189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ、だから{user}さん\nライブの前はずっとそわそわしてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haha‚ so that's why {user}-san\nwas so fidgety before the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2,
      "endTime": 132.3160318749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "パーティー中のサプライズ第一弾、成功！\nそれじゃあ第二弾、行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first surprise of the party‚ success!\nNow for the second part‚ let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5333333333,
      "endTime": 138.7524949801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
