    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "本当にありがとう。こんなに幸せなクリスマスは初めて\nこれからも、五人で頑張っていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much. This is the happiest Christmas I've ever had.\nLet's keep working hard together‚ all five of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.4333333333,
      "endTime": 333.26765042430003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "うん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.4666666667,
      "endTime": 334.5000000715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、せっかくだから、もう一回だけお祝いしない？\nパーティーの始めに言ったきりだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ since we're here‚ why don't we celebrate one more time?\nWe only said it at the start of the party.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 334.8333333333,
      "endTime": 341.9600667317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね。それではクラッカーの予備を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a good idea. Let me bring more crackers…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.1666666667,
      "endTime": 346.0068027656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、お祝いする瞬間に一緒にジャンプしよっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ shall we jump together at the moment of celebration?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.2,
      "endTime": 350.6866211891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "それは年越しでするものですわよね……！？\nよくいますけれど、そういう人",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't that something you do for New Year's……!?\nYou often see people doing that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.9,
      "endTime": 357.1451820149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……やっぱり月ストのみんなといるのは楽しいね\n琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… Being with everyone from Moon Tempest is always so fun.\nKotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.3333333333,
      "endTime": 363.5666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2212_01_05-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you're right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.8333333333,
      "endTime": 366.1313958247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
